        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-21",
        "text": "09 March, 1940 -",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 17.908,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": -102.83,
          "y_mm": 33.266
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-23",
        "text": "Fill not your hearts with pain and sorrow, but remember me in every tomorrow.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_mm": 15.715,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0.796,
          "y_mm": 59.285
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-25",
        "text": "Remember the joy, the laughter, the smiles, I&apos;ve only gone to rest for a little while.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_mm": 15.602,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": -2.308,
          "y_mm": 77.505
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-27",
        "text": "As long as I have the love of each of you, I can live in the hearts of all of you.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_mm": 15.775,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 1.003,
          "y_mm": 146.022
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-29",
        "text": "Nenes dhe Babes tone to dashur",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_mm": 18.83,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 5.514,
          "y_mm": 165.339
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-31",
        "text": "So dry your eyes and remember me, not as I am now, but as I used to be.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_mm": 16.001,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0.812,
          "y_mm": 96.144
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-32",
        "text": "Because, I will remember you all and look on with a smile.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_mm": 16.219,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": -2.104,
          "y_mm": 113.029
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-33",
        "text": "Understand in your hearts, I&apos;ve only gone to rest a little while.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_mm": 15.948,
